# Telegram Gemini Bot

Simple Telegram bot that connects to Google Gemini AI.

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
pip install python-telegram-bot aiohttp requests

2. Open bot.py and replace:
- YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN_HERE with token from @BotFather
- YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE with key from Google AI Studio

3. Run the bot:
python bot.py

## Usage
- Send any message to get Gemini response
- /start - welcome message
- /help - joke help

## Note
MVP version - no extra features included.